snippet.textDisplay: Everything I've been saying about Wilder and his one dimensional right hand, it works until it don't work. Wilder should fire those two useless trainers and get somebody that can teach him to move his head and feet, in order to throw punches from different angles while at the same time avoiding being punched, balanced on his feet. In other words Wilder needs to raise his athleticism and agility because dude is stiff and awkward as hell. It's almost criminal for his two trainers to have been working his corner for all these years and not have helped him to improve his skills by tightening up his weaknesses.
